# Greeting
- Hey
- Hi

# TimeOfDayWithCondition
- IF: @{time == 'morning'}
    - @{Greeting()} Morning
- ELSEIF: @{time == 'evening'}
    - @{Greeting()} Evening
- ELSE:
    - @{Greeting()} Afternoon

# greetInAWeek
- SWITCH: @{day}
    - CASE: @{'Saturday'}
        - Happy Saturday!
        - Nice Saturday!
    - CASE: @{'Sunday'}
        - Happy Sunday!
        - Nice Sunday!
    - DEFAULT:
        - Work Hard!
        - Weekend soon!